Ingredients - Class in game
Ingredients can be picked up and have their own icons on the grid, extends the interactions class The ingredients are: onion, squirrel, rotten tomato, rabbit, smelly cheese, radioactive slime
Ingredients(PApplet, int, int, int) - Constructor for class game.Ingredients
creates a new ingredient based off the integer assigned for the name 1-onion, 2-squirrel, 3-tomato, 4-rabbit, 5-cheese, 6-slime
